settings.description: the end of the line is now here. one final half of Bowser's newest castle awaits, and it's filled to the brim with bros! think you can take down the king in this dangerous trek?
just like how the real e-reader levels have a two part special that's all about one tough as nails challenge.. instead of an airship, you get a huge castle! watch out, The Big Boo awaits you!
